* Iron Raptor keeps a steady pace because she wanted Prowl and herself 
inside of the CF as soon as they could be and it would still be a few min at 
the pace they were going. But she was willing to take this time to help 
Prowl get his feet under him and hoped he would forgive her for breaking his 
wing in SBM.
She could tell that he was pretty shaken up and she rubbed his side a bit.
< Looks like you got one when I got mine back, babe."
She smiled at him all the same.
It was a powerful mode and she was sure that if he could just get controle 
of it he'd be something to be feared in battles, and her thoughts relayed 
that too.
< Think you can stay awake?>
Iron Raptor didn't really want him sleeping but she could take a mega cycle 
or two for him to rest and relax in his quarters before she got him down to 
work on what she had in mind.
It was about the right time to get down to his plan.*
